reviewText: Rodeo Bloopers 10 DVD - and rated it a 1 star because there as no zero star option. It was advertised as a great 'party video'. Advertising as a party video is a misrepresentation as I've not attended a party nor thrown a party for 30 min. in duration. Secondly, while I admit I enjoy the thrill of rodeo - an extremley dangerous sport, the events filmed in the video were failures, not bloopers. There were a couple of humorous events, but there was approx. 15 minutes of extremely boring 'acting' by some gentlemen trying to be funny - but they were ridculous, so also, don't waste your money, or time on Rodeo Bloopers 10. It sucked so much, I had to throw it out in the recycle so I can say, "That's annoying" and it was boring and I would not recommend buying that DVD, it was yucky, dark and light changes, and both are silly crap of bull and there's team roping in Rodeo Bloopers 10, so, forget team roping and just stick with rodeo's only real three main events of calf roping steer wrestling and bull riding as the real true done deal, and let the cowgirls compete with the men in calf roping and bull riding as the real true done deal, got it? Save more of your time and money on mostly the real four products I recommend of: Rodeo Bloopers 8 - DVD Rodeo Bloopers 9 - DVD Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 1 - DVD Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 2 - DVD You'll love Rodeo Bloopers 8 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers 9 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 1 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 2 - DVD because these are much better and I would totally recommend those four of the real Rodeo Bloopers as the real true done deal as four of them are all the real thing and a much better choice, so stick with and take my advice and pass on the it and say Bloopers 10 never should've been made and should be history, so, just stick with Rodeo Bloopers 8 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers 9 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 1 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 2 - DVD, got it and understood, but the only ones that kick into high gear that are a cinimatic masterpiece are just Rodeo Bloopers 8 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers 9 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 1 - DVD,Rodeo Bloopers Collector's Edition 2 - DVD, OK?

I may not be a cowboy myself, but this is one heck of a very funny and enteratining video. It has wonderful songs as well as just great musical sequences that people can exercise to. I do that on my treadmill. The music has great rhythm to it. By the time this tape is over I break out into a cool sweat. I bet that my friends who actually are cowboys themselves would love this video also. Any action fan should certainly own this.
